---
title: Cheesy Plant-Based Mince Ragu & Fettuccine with Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Parsley
description: Indulge in this plant-based delight where savoury plant-based mince is simmered to perfection in a rich, flavourful tomato
sauce. Paired with slurpable fettuccine, this wholesome dish offers a hearty and satisfying experience that proves plant-based
eating can be both delicious and comforting.

*We’ve replaced the spaghetti in this recipe with fettuccine due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/675bc72ec16ec378c8405ab4-61a9bc8b.jpeg
